7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"How To Get Iso Certification For A Small Company"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:31:56+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"There is always some kind of hestitation for small business owners when it comes to getting ISO certification. Read this blog further to know how to get ISO"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How to get ISO 9001 Certification for a small company?"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Ever since the introduction of the ISO standards, it has become inevitable industrial ethics for the implementation of a Quality Management System or QMS across the globe. However, there are still loads of small business owners and entrepreneurs who assume that ISO 9001 the certification that's solely relevant for larger business corporations. this is often because of the actual fact that there's a way of perceived and comprehended complexity and convolution related to this certification that deters the small business owners and entrepreneurs from opting for ISO 9001. However, it's time that the small business owners and entrepreneurs change their minds about the feeling of intimidation and apprehension that they experience once it comes to getting an ISO 9001 certification."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"One thing that plenty of small business owners and entrepreneurs miss to understand is that ISO 9001 certification is just a chance for enhancing the standards by documenting and improving the prevailing systems and processes that an organization already has in the first place. In fact, having the ISO 9001 - QMS implemented for a small business can really improve and help to boost its brand reputation and grow over time."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Let’s now clarify some misconceptions about getting ISO certification for small businesses and what's hindering when it comes to the successful implementation of ISO certification. This could really help the small business owners and entrepreneurs develop a much better plan about How to get ISO certification for their small scale business and how to proceed with the process once they are ready."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"A common misbelief that hinders small business owners from the idea of getting ISO certification in the first place is that many people assume that the auditing method for ISO certification is extremely strict and rigid. If in case you get rejected by the auditor you can't get or apply for ISO certification again. However, this is often misconceived and it is far from reality. It's not really about failing the auditing methods and processes that one should be upset about. Auditor who evaluates QMS will examine whether the business's standard aligns with the recommendations & standard set by the ISO. In case they notice that business fail to fulfill the necessities in any process or method, they will allow you to know how to address the problems and how to fix them in order to get ISO certification for their business. Therefore, just because failing to pass the audit, it doesn't necessarily mean it is the end of the world."}],"$L10","$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16"]}],"$L17"]}]}]
